    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver for someone prioritizing function. While the engine and transmission are in good working order, the exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the cabin is clean but shows significant wear on the driver's seat upholstery and some of the plastic trim. It has been regularly maintained, though it will likely need minor suspension work and new tires in the near future. Overall, it's a solid, honest car that gets the job done but is far from a showpiece.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in concours-level condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface reflects meticulous stewardship, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine, showroom-quality cabin. Mechanically, the vehicle operates with the precision of its initial delivery, having undergone a rigorous multi-point certification to ensure peak performance. This is an exemplary specimen for the discerning collector who demands uncompromising aesthetic and mechanical integrity.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It is honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have babied this car since day one\u2014always kept in the garage and polished to perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and looks even better in person. I am truly sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a benchmark-condition 2005 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six. This specimen boasts a meticulously maintained VANOS system and factory-spec individual throttle bodies, ensuring linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission provides surgical shift precision, paired with a perfectly functioning M-Variable limited-slip differential. Chassis integrity is paramount; this vehicle has undergone documented rear subframe reinforcement and retains its original suspension geometry with no bushing play. Finished in original Alpine White over Nappa leather, the aesthetics are commensurate with its mechanical excellence. This is a turn-key, collector-grade example with a comprehensive service dossier and zero deferred maintenance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2022 model. Immaculate condition. Zero mechanical issues. Clean title. Garage kept. Non-smoker. Inspection reports available.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true showroom-quality example that presents as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings, further protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is an immaculate time capsule; the premium leather seats remain firm and matte, showing no signs of bolster wear or aging, and the original 'new car' scent persists. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless, backed by a comprehensive binder containing every service record from day one. It has been strictly garage-kept under a breathable cover and has never seen rain or inclement weather. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature operates with factory precision. For the collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this vehicle stands as the gold standard of its class.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting an exemplary specimen of automotive excellence, this vehicle arrives in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. Meticulously maintained and preserved to the highest standards, it offers a peerless driving experience for the discerning collector. Every detail, from the pristine upholstery to the flawless mechanical synchronization, reflects a legacy of uncompromising care. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends standard market offerings, representing the pinnacle of its class.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly won't find another one like this. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and it looks just as stunning as the day it rolled off the lot. It's been pampered, garage-kept, and is basically in showroom condition. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an uncompromising E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 power plant, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanically, this chassis is fully sorted: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the dual-VANOS system has been overhauled with Beisan components. Rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the communicative steering rack remains razor-sharp. Zero fluid leaks, no VANOS rattle, and a flawless interior. This is a turn-key, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 43500.0,
